{"id": "1255628728659087641", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "> *人生不過是一個行走的影子，一個可憐的戲子。在舞台上高談闊論，並從此杳無音訊。這是個傻子所述的故事，說得慷慨激昂，卻毫無意義。*\n——《馬克白》莎士比亞\n　　深海界域的喚醒體掌握大海與幻夢，血肉界域則能操控肉體變化，超維界域可以創造並統治屬於他們的超維空間。而謬妄界域的喚醒體，能擾亂秩序與法則，他們或看見、或享受、或散播荒誕與悖謬，模糊現實與虛假。此刻你是觀眾，欣賞並分析著世界；彼時你是演員，為世界獻上激情與理想。但這有什麼用呢？世界不為你演出，世界也不為你駐目，一切皆是徒勞，就連感到徒勞本身也是徒勞。\n\n# 界域機制\n## 幕\n　　關卡開始時，進入**「開幕」**狀態。回合開始時，若處於**「開幕」**狀態下，且**「喝采」**（見下文）層數達到__ 10 層或以上__時，將切換至**「謝幕」**狀態；若處於**「謝幕」**狀態下，且**「喝采」**__層數為 0__ ，則會切換為**「開幕」**狀態。\n　　處於**「開幕」**狀態時，每回合開始時獲得__ 最大生命值2% 的護盾__，且指令卡中的**「開幕」**字段始生效；處於**「謝幕」**狀態時，獲得__ 隊伍總攻擊力2.5% 的力量__，且指令卡中的**「謝幕」**字段始生效。\n　　每 1 點界域精通使**「開幕」**狀態獲得的護盾提升 0.015% 最大生命值，以及使**「謝幕」**狀態獲得的力量提升 0.02% 的隊伍總攻擊力。\n\n## 喝采\n　　**「開幕」**狀態下，每次使用指令卡時，有 20% 的機率獲得 1 層**「喝采」**。若使用指令卡後沒有獲得**「喝采」**，則會使該機率提升 5% ，因使用指令卡而獲得**「喝采」**後將該機率復原至 15% 。戰鬥結束將繼承 50% 的**「喝采」**層數。\n　　**界域共生**：隊伍中每個混沌界域喚醒體，使戰鬥結束時繼承的**「喝采」**層數提升12%。渾沌界域喚醒體使用狂氣爆發時，額外獲得 1 層**「喝采」**。\n\n## 界域刻印\n**高潮**：獲得1層**「喝采」**。\n**高級高潮**：獲得2層**「喝采」**。\n\n## 界域造物\n> 白銀造物\n**蒼白面具**：每使用 6 張牌，獲得 1 層**「喝采」**。\n*陌生人將它贈予你，如同那陌生人的臉龐，完美無瑕、一體成型。*\n\n**翡翠曼荼羅**：切換為**「謝幕」**所需的**「喝采」**增加 2 層。每當切換**「幕」**時，獲得 2 層**「喝采」**。\n*池中蓮花大如車輪。大放異彩黃色星宿黃光。微妙香潔。其佛國土成就如是功德莊嚴。*\n\n**鹿首頭套**：回合結束時，**「開幕」**：每有 1 層**「喝采」**，獲得 6 點護盾。回合開始時，**「謝幕」**：每有 1 層**「喝采」**，獲得 9 點臨時力量。\n*寒風之中唯有飢餓相伴，透過鹿的眼窩你看見了嘲弄的觀眾，肚子咕嚕咕嚕地鼓掌，你知道導演會允許你在片場偷吃點零嘴的。*\n\n**傾頹磚石**：拾取時選擇一張指令卡刪除。回合開始時，**「謝幕」**：將該牌的原始複製置入手牌中，並使其獲得__消耗__與__虛無__。\n*失敗者凱旋而歸，崩塌的城牆後是祂繁盛的國，沉默地呼喚祂的名字，無處可去的祂便來到你的身邊。*\n\n> 黃金造物\n**襤褸王袍**：每次獲得**「喝采」**時，回復 12 點生命並獲得 1 算力，每回合最多觸發 3 次。打出症狀卡時，也可以進行獲得**「喝采」**的判定。\n*從凍餓窮人那邊奪來華羽彩霓，從此往前一站便是萬人之王，哪怕臣民們拍手嘲笑，你知道身為王族，你才是那個獨坐貴賓席的觀眾。*\n\n**真皮教典**：每次使用牌時，若該牌通過**「喝采」**判定，將該牌從棄牌堆置入手牌中，並使其算力消耗減少 1 直到下次使用該牌。\n*喜鵲啾啾讀著書，喜鵲抬頭望向你，喜鵲看著梳妝鏡，喜鵲今兒又有大餐吃。*\n\n> 詛咒造物\n**黃印**：拾取時獲得 2 張 3 選 1 隨機症狀卡。牌堆中每有 1 張症狀卡，使切換為**「謝幕」**所需的**「喝采」**層數增加 1 層。界域精通提升 40% 。\n*你夢見腫脹的信使向你傳下諭令，你夢見黑色的馬車嘎嘎駛來。冰冷的石料將你驚醒，隔壁的鄰居已經坐上靈車走了。*\n\n## 電梯\n> 攻擊型角色\n[孚士德](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1255629492945162320)\n[伊娃](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1255633606533976329)\n[莎莉娜](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1263212812721721444)\n> 防禦型角色\n[威爾斯](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1255629697358893136)\n[阿里翁](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1255635770392445009)\n[何馨](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1263214474307833947)\n> 輔助型角色\n[關雎](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1255636883908857977)\n[魏雁足](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1255629160760737813)\n[瑟拉](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1255628728659087641/1263663256778838046)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:00:17.366000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-19T01:08:23.595000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "yellow_sign", "emoji_id": "1124789636103938128", "count": 12}, {"emoji": "🥺", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Sendflowers", "emoji_id": "1400771545370067118", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1255629160760737813", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```\n油彩的味道，石料的冰冷。倘若關雎坐在那兒一動不動，很容易就會被誤認為是尊雕像，一個藝術品。\n他通曉音律，善作文章。他的作品就像他本人一樣，只要不動的話就會被認為是藝術品。\n但這一切的一切，所有的靈感與創作，對他而言就是一件事情，一個作品。一齣偉大的、悲壯的戲劇，你我都不過是其中的丑角罷了。誰不是呢？\n```\n角色立繪：我自己委託的OC。\n命輪圖示：[共濟會符號](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/freemasonry_3170346?term=freemasonry&page=1&position=12&origin=tag&related_id=3170346)、[黃印](https://lovecraft.fandom.com/wiki/Yellow_Sign?file=The_Yellow_Sign.jpg)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:02:00.387000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1255629160853016626", "filename": "579539feb7806f2d.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 27173, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629160853016626/579539feb7806f2d.jpg?ex=69cb8d88&is=69ca3c08&hm=7c0044f19e32c3214d0086a22ed4d20895aeae0986620c01f9d98db968768aad&"}, {"id": "1255629161171652708", "filename": "a98e5ecf9e553abf.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 134245, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629161171652708/a98e5ecf9e553abf.jpg?ex=69cb8d88&is=69ca3c08&hm=da48097ecb19abb50a03e3c090382d369dbde77b78c084d0be936a1009772bf0&"}, {"id": "1255629161565913128", "filename": "596697441f20df47.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 144263, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629161565913128/596697441f20df47.jpg?ex=69cb8d88&is=69ca3c08&hm=e3ab30d94ac4f31b5ae406b41d288d25914439a07c8268fe01cedbc7672feff4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1255629492945162320", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```　　他深入過叢林與極地，他在最高的山與最深的海下留下過足跡，他體會過至高的快樂與至苦的痛楚。他與敵人跟夥伴狂歡，他樂於嚐試所有公正與褻瀆的活動，甘苦的啤酒、酸甜的紅酒，以及鮮美的血液全不在話下。\n　　他是未知的先驅、神秘的飛蛾，引領眾人前往無法回頭的一瞬間，撲向通往地獄的烈火中。他是快樂的奴隸。```\n角色立繪：[AI製圖](https://www.pinterest.com/pin/3870349673327823/)\n命輪圖示：[油燈](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/lanterns_4954886?term=oil+lamp&page=1&position=16&origin=tag&related_id=4954886)、[蛾](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/moth_1357433?term=moth&page=1&position=5&origin=search&related_id=1357433)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:03:19.586000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "huh1", "emoji_id": "1356053088552747141", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255629493033238699", "filename": "802ffb4293e2293b.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 23554, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629493033238699/802ffb4293e2293b.jpg?ex=69cb8dd7&is=69ca3c57&hm=f44bbd96af70d7f00119cd5e546e36b422c19a3891e666fe21acd1e27837e41a&"}, {"id": "1255629493297614938", "filename": "f53cddb1d2bb2b1b.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 132101, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629493297614938/f53cddb1d2bb2b1b.jpg?ex=69cb8dd7&is=69ca3c57&hm=32928cba40994130a1c2485d4a6e4702a0915d3124481bc3b6517a8fd154c6ec&"}, {"id": "1255629493520044092", "filename": "6906cf1c0bc092a4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 143880, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629493520044092/6906cf1c0bc092a4.jpg?ex=69cb8dd7&is=69ca3c57&hm=019276d7496f6bdeabf803ba18cb0b6dfda46ee814498ee7a22490aa3da6df6a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1255629697358893136", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```他的聲名遠播，他的家財萬貫，這是百年以來他對世人救濟的輝煌成果。當你身陷水火之中，只需高呼他的名字，以最卑微的姿態向他求助，慈悲為懷的大善人威爾斯會不吝代價地救你於苦難中。\n你只需要負責感激涕零，銘記他的功勞，讚頌他的美德。即使是這麼微小的報答，彌薩格大學也未曾向他求取任何資助，或許永遠不會。```\n角色立繪：[AI製圖](https://www.pinterest.com/pin/492649952816373/)\n風味文字：[翡翠喇嘛說星宿光佛經](https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv23849063/)\n命輪圖示：[符號](https://www.shutterstock.com/zh/image-vector/poster-two-color-versions-byakhee-starsteed-2001220049)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:04:08.322000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1255629697690112011", "filename": "170bc6330a83a5f3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 22721, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629697690112011/170bc6330a83a5f3.jpg?ex=69cb8e08&is=69ca3c88&hm=64bf4ab52a95136b21f25d4c80d27cd306ceebae352cd90c5d106aa8eee2ae79&"}, {"id": "1255629698004680725", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 125316, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629698004680725/1.jpg?ex=69cb8e08&is=69ca3c88&hm=9fb28025c2b501b343145068a6126eb609e8021c88601e8552a9c199981d64a9&"}, {"id": "1255629698420178964", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 146453, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255629698420178964/1.jpg?ex=69cb8e08&is=69ca3c88&hm=2c613385a9c06caebe62f5f669014e2029267c1fb2639c1e4aac9c7901491cc4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1255633606533976329", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```「有沒有人要買火柴？」稚氣未脫的聲音在寒冬中響起，那是個面黃肌瘦的女孩，她的到來捲起陣陣飛雪，祈求著一份餐食；她的離去留下餓殍橫街，今天依舊是吃不飽穿不暖的苦日子。但沒事的，對飽暖的憧憬支持著她往前走，這是希望的火光，是人們前進的動力。```\n角色立繪：[AI製圖](https://creator.nightcafe.studio/creation/tICaaI1TRtKOURFHTT06)\n命輪圖示：[火柴](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/matches_5363604?term=fire+matches&related_id=5363604)、[鹿頭](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/antler_13372396?related_id=13372396)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:19:40.342000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:20:02.504000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1255633606664130570", "filename": "c1d366d6d1bda4f2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 25918, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255633606664130570/c1d366d6d1bda4f2.jpg?ex=69cb91ac&is=69ca402c&hm=ee94aafadf23012da1924d1bce4c45b13a3c83a067c9b6b8af96a93280b0cd7b&"}, {"id": "1255633606995607633", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131895, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255633606995607633/1.jpg?ex=69cb91ac&is=69ca402c&hm=a23316a378415059643f3df0d07a34b0a251b2e4f2cbeefb3d68610cd16fc7ea&"}, {"id": "1255633607259721808", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 152533, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255633607259721808/2.jpg?ex=69cb91ac&is=69ca402c&hm=9ad0fddaa79ee76448095ce4307d352018d9cc25cebf4d755566d82678dbce47&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1255635770392445009", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```他是市政府的清潔工，是銀行的警衛、是警局的看守與濟貧院的送奶工。她可以是任何人，只要下達命令，既可以是你最得力的助手，也可以是追獵你的殺手。至少目前，她依然對大學保持善意，以風馳電掣的效率消化著任務。但那份忠心屬於誰，或許最好不要問出口。```\n角色立繪：[KkKax的作品](https://www.artstation.com/artwork/KkKax)\n命輪圖示：[酒瓶](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/mead_5840658?term=mead&page=1&position=10&origin=search&related_id=5840658)、[銀河](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/milky-way_3026429?term=milky+way&page=1&position=30&origin=search&related_id=3026429)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:28:16.246000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1255635770631389195", "filename": "3dd5e95fee92d750.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 22327, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255635770631389195/3dd5e95fee92d750.jpg?ex=69cb93b0&is=69ca4230&hm=effe7dd6ea9543d519c52c344a41da1bf7950bf28541a36b6535cffb8c3df1b9&"}, {"id": "1255635770891567238", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 129925, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255635770891567238/2.jpg?ex=69cb93b0&is=69ca4230&hm=cab58330f9e0da91d7fd6b55bb7145d41afa3563d18f2e4ab785465f06a703d4&"}, {"id": "1255635771239436398", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 135234, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255635771239436398/3.jpg?ex=69cb93b0&is=69ca4230&hm=12103811350e0ca3692107db66edcfef48d96ac3acdc751d0ff950d7fec08847&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1255636883908857977", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```他總是懷抱著各式各樣的疑問，對天文地理、對社會政治、對融蝕、對人性。活脫脫就是個孩子，但千萬不能這麼說他，因為就連那份彆扭也跟小孩子一樣，卻帶著二三十年訓練的身手與槍法。```\n角色立繪：[AI製圖](https://www.pinterest.com/pin/8655424279212656/)\n命輪圖示：[鑰匙](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/key_2647399?term=key&related_id=2647399)、[乳房](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/breastfeeding_941500?term=breast&page=1&position=65&origin=search&related_id=941500)", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T21:32:41.729000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255636883975831612", "filename": "440d8be4445b6f0d.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 20615, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255636883975831612/440d8be4445b6f0d.jpg?ex=69cb94b9&is=69ca4339&hm=6269bd56a1f88b7231a6962cc063ebd4f1c33303a3cf8019a0206b158aaef43e&"}, {"id": "1255636884290535515", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 132142, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255636884290535515/3.jpg?ex=69cb94b9&is=69ca4339&hm=c2fe71eba25d37d0169c04ec504e92d7ff5fc293835a0d6682a6045da4e99393&"}, {"id": "1255636884558975048", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 151373, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1255636884558975048/4.jpg?ex=69cb94b9&is=69ca4339&hm=ecde881d03323585c21184e88ccfb02828ffc8485ca6f9667d84359e77bb6029&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
